/*
 * AILang Agentic v0.2.0
 * MAL (Meta Attack Language) DSL for Generative AI / Agentic AI Systems
 *
 * Coverage:
 *   - MITRE ATLAS v5.4 (16 tactics, 155 techniques, 35 mitigations)
 *   - OWASP LLM Top 10 2025 (LLM01–LLM10)
 *   - OWASP Securing Agentic Applications Guide 1.0 (T1–T15, KC1–KC6)
 *   - ISO/IEC 5339:2024 (AI lifecycle, trustworthiness)
 *
 * Assets: 15 (3 abstract + 12 concrete)
 * Attack Steps: 130+
 * Defenses: 50+
 * Associations: 22
 *
 * Generated: 2026-03-25
 * Methodology: Prompt - Case_1_v0.1.txt (6-step MAL creation methodology)
 */

#id: "com.security.ailang.agentic"
#version: "0.2.0"

// ============================================================
// CATEGORY: AIFoundation
// Base abstract assets shared across all AI components
// ============================================================

category AIFoundation {

    // Abstract base asset for all AI system components
    // Provides common attack surface and defense primitives
    abstract asset AIComponent {

        | exploit
            user info: "AI 컴포넌트에 대한 일반적인 취약점 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0000 계열)"
            developer info: "Base exploit step inherited by all AI components"
            -> compromise

        | validAccountAccess
            user info: "유효한 계정/자격증명을 통한 정상적 접근 경로 악용 (ATLAS AML.T0012)"
            developer info: "Adversary uses valid credentials to access AI component"
            -> compromise

        | compromise
            user info: "AI 컴포넌트가 완전히 침해된 상태"
            developer info: "Final compromise state — reached from multiple attack paths"

        # accessControl
            user info: "접근 제어 메커니즘 (인증, 인가, 최소권한 원칙)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0001 Limit Model Artifact Release, M0018 User Training"
            -> exploit, validAccountAccess

        # telemetryLogging
            user info: "행동 모니터링 및 감사 로그 수집"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0020 Adversarial Detection, M0021 ML Model Audit Logging"
            -> compromise
    }
}

// ============================================================
// CATEGORY: GenerativeAI
// Core generative AI model assets and supporting data
// ============================================================

category GenerativeAI {

    // Large Language Model / Foundation Model
    // Primary attack surface for prompt-based attacks
    // OWASP LLM01, LLM02, LLM04, LLM06, LLM07, LLM09, LLM10
    asset GenerativeLanguageModel extends AIComponent {

        | directPromptInjection
            user info: "사용자가 직접 악의적 명령을 프롬프트에 삽입 (OWASP LLM01, ATLAS AML.T0051.000)"
            developer info: "Attacker directly manipulates LLM via crafted user input"
            -> overrideSystemPrompt, generateHarmfulContent, extractSystemPrompt

        | indirectPromptInjection
            user info: "외부 데이터 소스(웹페이지, 문서 등)를 통한 간접적 명령 삽입 (ATLAS AML.T0051.001)"
            developer info: "Malicious content in retrieved documents triggers unintended LLM behavior"
            -> triggerAgentAction, trustedOutputManipulation, dataLeakage

        | triggeredPromptInjection
            user info: "특정 조건이나 컨텍스트에서만 활성화되는 지연 실행 프롬프트 인젝션"
            developer info: "Delayed/conditional injection — activates on specific trigger context"
            -> delayExecution, triggerAgentAction

        | jailbreak
            user info: "안전 가이드라인 및 정렬 제약을 우회하는 탈옥 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0054, OWASP LLM01)"
            developer info: "Bypasses model safety training and content filters"
            -> bypassSafetyGuardrails, generateHarmfulContent, generateMaliciousCommands

        | promptObfuscation
            user info: "탐지 회피를 위한 프롬프트 난독화 (Base64, 암호화, 동음이의어 등) (ATLAS AML.T0049)"
            developer info: "Encoded/obfuscated prompts evade content-based filters"
            -> bypassSafetyGuardrails, jailbreak

        | promptCrafting
            user info: "LLM 동작을 조작하기 위한 정교한 프롬프트 설계 (ATLAS AML.T0040)"
            developer info: "Adversary crafts prompts specifically to elicit unintended model behavior"
            -> directPromptInjection, jailbreak, extractSystemPrompt

        | overrideSystemPrompt
            user info: "시스템 프롬프트 덮어쓰기 또는 무력화 (OWASP LLM07, ATLAS AML.T0051)"
            developer info: "Attacker overrides system-level instructions with adversarial ones"
            -> generateHarmfulContent, generateMaliciousCommands

        | bypassSafetyGuardrails
            user info: "안전 필터 및 콘텐츠 정책 우회 (OWASP LLM01, ATLAS AML.T0054)"
            developer info: "Content safety mechanisms disabled or circumvented"
            -> generateHarmfulContent, generateMaliciousCommands

        | generateHarmfulContent
            user info: "유해 콘텐츠, 허위정보, 사회공학 콘텐츠 생성 (OWASP LLM09, ATLAS AML.T0044)"
            developer info: "LLM produces harmful, false, or dangerous output at adversary direction"

        | generateMaliciousCommands
            user info: "악성 코드, 익스플로잇, 사이버 공격 명령 생성 (ATLAS AML.T0044.000)"
            developer info: "LLM generates usable attack payloads or malicious scripts"
            -> triggerAgentAction

        | triggerAgentAction
            user info: "에이전트 도구 호출 또는 자율 행동 유발 (OWASP LLM06, ATLAS AML.T0080)"
            developer info: "LLM triggers downstream agent actions via manipulated reasoning"

        | extractSystemPrompt
            user info: "기밀 시스템 프롬프트 내용 추출 (OWASP LLM07, ATLAS AML.T0056.004)"
            developer info: "Attacker extracts confidential system prompt instructions"
            -> systemPromptLeakage

        | systemPromptLeakage
            user info: "시스템 프롬프트 기밀 정보 노출 (OWASP LLM07)"
            developer info: "Disclosed system prompt reveals internal configurations, personas, or secrets"

        | dataLeakage
            user info: "학습 데이터 또는 컨텍스트 내 민감 정보 유출 (OWASP LLM02, ATLAS AML.T0024)"
            developer info: "PII, secrets, or confidential context leaked through LLM output"

        | trustedOutputManipulation
            user info: "신뢰할 수 있는 것처럼 보이는 조작된 출력 생성 (ATLAS AML.T0048)"
            developer info: "Adversary causes LLM to produce outputs that appear authoritative or trustworthy"
            -> citationManipulation

        | citationManipulation
            user info: "허위 인용 또는 환각된 출처 생성으로 신뢰성 조작 (OWASP LLM09)"
            developer info: "LLM cites non-existent sources or fabricates authoritative references"

        | maliciousResponseRendering
            user info: "악성 콘텐츠가 포함된 응답을 클라이언트에서 렌더링 유도 (OWASP LLM05)"
            developer info: "LLM output contains XSS, injected scripts, or unsafe content for downstream rendering"

        | promptSelfReplication
            user info: "프롬프트 인젝션을 통한 자기 복제 공격 전파 (ATLAS AML.T0051.002)"
            developer info: "Prompt injection causes the LLM to replicate the malicious payload to other contexts"

        | manipulateChatHistory
            user info: "대화 이력 조작으로 컨텍스트 오염 (OWASP Agentic T9, ATLAS AML.T0080)"
            developer info: "Chat history poisoned to create false context for subsequent interactions"

        | delayExecution
            user info: "미래의 특정 시점에 활성화되는 지연 명령 삽입 (ATLAS AML.T0080.002)"
            developer info: "Time-delayed or condition-triggered execution of adversarial instructions"

        | discoverHallucinations
            user info: "환각 취약점 탐색 및 패키지 혼동 공격 준비 (ATLAS AML.T0056.001)"
            developer info: "Attacker probes for hallucinated package names or APIs to exploit"
            -> exploitHallucinatedPackages

        | exploitHallucinatedPackages
            user info: "환각된 패키지명을 악용한 의존성 혼동 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0019.002)"
            developer info: "Attacker publishes malicious package matching LLM-hallucinated name"

        | denialOfService
            user info: "LLM 서비스 거부 공격 (토큰 폭탄, 재귀 프롬프트 등) (OWASP LLM10, ATLAS AML.T0029)"
            developer info: "Resource exhaustion via crafted prompts (token flooding, recursive expansions)"

        | costHarvesting
            user info: "API 호출 비용 과다 발생을 통한 경제적 피해 (OWASP LLM10)"
            developer info: "Attacker deliberately triggers expensive API calls to cause financial damage"

        | inferTrainingDataMembership
            user info: "학습 데이터 멤버십 추론 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0024.000)"
            developer info: "Membership inference attack to determine if specific data was in training set"

        | inferenceAPIExfiltration
            user info: "추론 API를 통한 모델 또는 데이터 유출 (ATLAS AML.T0040.000)"
            developer info: "Systematic querying of inference API to extract model knowledge or training data"

        | discoverSystemInfo
            user info: "시스템 구성, 버전, 배포 정보 탐색 (ATLAS AML.T0007)"
            developer info: "Reconnaissance to gather info about underlying AI infrastructure"

        | specialCharacterProbing
            user info: "특수문자를 이용한 필터 우회 탐색 (ATLAS AML.T0049.001)"
            developer info: "Testing special characters, delimiters, and encoding to bypass input filters"
            -> bypassSafetyGuardrails

        | systemKeywordProbing
            user info: "시스템 키워드 및 내부 명령어 탐색 (ATLAS AML.T0056.004)"
            developer info: "Probing for internal keywords that reveal system prompt or trigger special behavior"
            -> extractSystemPrompt

        # guardrails
            user info: "입력/출력 가드레일 (콘텐츠 필터, 안전 분류기)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0004 Restrict Number of ML Model Queries, M0002 Passive ML Output Obfuscation"
            -> directPromptInjection, indirectPromptInjection, jailbreak, promptObfuscation,
               bypassSafetyGuardrails, maliciousResponseRendering, promptSelfReplication,
               discoverHallucinations, specialCharacterProbing

        # safetyGuidelines
            user info: "안전 가이드라인 및 사용 정책 (ATLAS M0005)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0005 Control Access to ML Models, M0016 Vulnerability Scanning"
            -> jailbreak, bypassSafetyGuardrails, generateHarmfulContent, generateMaliciousCommands

        # modelAlignment
            user info: "RLHF 등 모델 정렬 기법 (ATLAS M0008)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0008 Validate ML Model, M0019 Encrypt Sensitive Information"
            -> jailbreak, generateHarmfulContent, trustedOutputManipulation, citationManipulation

        # rateLimiting
            user info: "API 요청 속도 제한 (ATLAS M0004)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0004 Restrict Number of ML Model Queries"
            -> denialOfService, costHarvesting, inferTrainingDataMembership, inferenceAPIExfiltration
    }

    // Embedding model for vectorization of text
    // Used in RAG pipelines and semantic search
    // OWASP LLM08, ATLAS AML.T0015
    asset EmbeddingModel extends AIComponent {

        | connect
            user info: "임베딩 모델 엔드포인트에 대한 초기 접근"
            developer info: "Initial access to embedding model API or service"
            -> invertEmbedding, evadeModel, poisonModel

        | invertEmbedding
            user info: "임베딩 벡터에서 원본 텍스트 역추론 (OWASP LLM08, ATLAS AML.T0024.002)"
            developer info: "Inversion attack to recover approximate original text from embedding vector"
            -> dataLeakage

        | dataLeakage
            user info: "임베딩 모델을 통한 민감 정보 유출"
            developer info: "Sensitive text fragments leaked through embedding similarity"

        | evadeModel
            user info: "임베딩 기반 유사도 탐지 우회 (ATLAS AML.T0015)"
            developer info: "Adversarial perturbation to evade similarity-based detection using embeddings"

        | poisonModel
            user info: "임베딩 모델 파인튜닝 데이터 오염 (ATLAS AML.T0018)"
            developer info: "Poison fine-tuning data to degrade embedding quality or insert backdoors"

        | extractModel
            user info: "임베딩 모델 파라미터 추출 (ATLAS AML.T0056.002)"
            developer info: "Model extraction attack via systematic API querying of embedding model"

        # modelHardening
            user info: "모델 강화 (적대적 학습, 입력 정규화)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0007 Sanitize Training Data, M0014 Verify ML Artifacts"
            -> invertEmbedding, evadeModel, poisonModel

        # outputObfuscation
            user info: "임베딩 출력 난독화 (노이즈 추가, 반올림)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0002 Passive ML Output Obfuscation"
            -> invertEmbedding, extractModel
    }

    // Training dataset for AI models
    // OWASP LLM04, ATLAS AML.T0018, AML.T0019
    asset TrainingData {

        | access
            user info: "학습 데이터셋에 대한 접근 획득"
            developer info: "Initial access to training data storage or pipeline"
            -> poison, membership_inference

        | poison
            user info: "학습 데이터 오염 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0018, OWASP LLM04)"
            developer info: "Adversarial data injected into training set to backdoor or degrade model"
            -> erodeIntegrity

        | erodeIntegrity
            user info: "데이터 무결성 침해로 모델 성능 저하 (ATLAS AML.T0018.000)"
            developer info: "Model trained on corrupted data produces unreliable outputs"
            -> publishPoisoned

        | publishPoisoned
            user info: "오염된 데이터셋을 공개 저장소에 배포 (ATLAS AML.T0019.000)"
            developer info: "Poisoned dataset published to trick others into using compromised training data"

        | membership_inference
            user info: "멤버십 추론으로 개인정보 포함 여부 확인 (ATLAS AML.T0024.000, OWASP LLM02)"
            developer info: "Attacker determines whether specific individuals' data was in training set"

        # dataSanitization
            user info: "학습 데이터 정제 및 검증 (ATLAS M0007)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0007 Sanitize Training Data"
            -> poison, erodeIntegrity

        # dataProvenance
            user info: "데이터 출처 추적 및 무결성 검증 (ATLAS M0013)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0013 Code Signing — adapted for data artifacts"
            -> poison, publishPoisoned

        # dataAccessControl
            user info: "학습 데이터 접근 제어 (ATLAS M0005)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0005 Control Access to ML Models"
            -> access, membership_inference
    }

    // Trained model artifact (weights, checkpoints, serialized models)
    // OWASP LLM03, ATLAS AML.T0010, AML.T0011
    asset ModelArtifact {

        | access
            user info: "모델 아티팩트 (가중치, 체크포인트) 접근"
            developer info: "Access to model files, weights, or serialized model objects"
            -> extractModel, manipulateModel

        | extractModel
            user info: "모델 가중치 또는 구조 추출 (ATLAS AML.T0056.002)"
            developer info: "Physical access to model weights enables full model extraction"

        | manipulateModel
            user info: "모델 파라미터 직접 조작 (ATLAS AML.T0011)"
            developer info: "Direct modification of model weights to alter behavior"
            -> backdoorInjection, corruptModel

        | backdoorInjection
            user info: "트리거 기반 백도어를 모델에 삽입 (ATLAS AML.T0018.001)"
            developer info: "Hidden trigger embedded in model causes specific malicious behavior when activated"

        | corruptModel
            user info: "모델 손상으로 서비스 거부 또는 오작동 유발 (ATLAS AML.T0031)"
            developer info: "Model weights corrupted to cause inference failures or denial of service"

        | embedMalware
            user info: "직렬화된 모델 파일에 악성코드 삽입 (ATLAS AML.T0011.000, OWASP LLM03)"
            developer info: "Malicious code embedded in pickle/safetensor files executes on load"

        | publishPoisoned
            user info: "손상된 모델을 공개 모델 허브에 배포 (ATLAS AML.T0019.001)"
            developer info: "Compromised model published to model hub to infect downstream users"

        # modelAccessControl
            user info: "모델 아티팩트 접근 제어 (ATLAS M0005)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0005 Control Access to ML Models, M0001 Limit Model Artifact Release"
            -> access, extractModel

        # artifactVerification
            user info: "모델 무결성 검증 (해시, 서명 확인) (ATLAS M0014)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0014 Verify ML Artifacts"
            -> manipulateModel, backdoorInjection, embedMalware

        # modelValidation
            user info: "배포 전 모델 동작 검증 (ATLAS M0008)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0008 Validate ML Model"
            -> backdoorInjection, corruptModel

        # codeSigning
            user info: "모델 아티팩트 코드 서명 (ATLAS M0013)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0013 Code Signing for model files"
            -> publishPoisoned, embedMalware
    }
}

// ============================================================
// CATEGORY: AgenticAI
// Agentic AI system components — orchestration, memory, tools
// ============================================================

category AgenticAI {

    // Orchestration engine coordinating multi-agent workflows
    // OWASP Agentic T1–T3, KC1, ATLAS AML.T0080
    asset OrchestrationEngine extends AIComponent {

        | connect
            user info: "오케스트레이션 엔진에 대한 초기 접근"
            developer info: "Initial network/API access to the orchestration layer"
            -> goalManipulation, identitySpoofing, communicationPoisoning

        | goalManipulation
            user info: "에이전트의 목표 또는 계획 조작 (OWASP Agentic T2, ATLAS AML.T0080)"
            developer info: "Adversary alters agent's high-level goals or task plan"
            -> manipulateChatHistory, obfuscateActionTrail

        | identitySpoofing
            user info: "다른 에이전트 또는 신뢰된 서비스로 위장 (OWASP Agentic T1)"
            developer info: "Attacker impersonates trusted agent identity to gain elevated trust"
            -> goalManipulation

        | manipulateChatHistory
            user info: "에이전트 대화 이력 조작으로 컨텍스트 오염 (OWASP Agentic T9)"
            developer info: "Chat history manipulation creates false context affecting agent decisions"

        | obfuscateActionTrail
            user info: "에이전트 행동 기록 은폐 및 감사 추적 방해 (ATLAS AML.T0054.003)"
            developer info: "Attacker obfuscates malicious agent actions to evade detection"

        | communicationPoisoning
            user info: "에이전트 간 통신 채널 오염 (OWASP Agentic T3)"
            developer info: "Adversary intercepts or modifies inter-agent messages"
            -> goalManipulation

        # componentSegmentation
            user info: "에이전트 컴포넌트 격리 및 최소권한 통신 (ATLAS M0022)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0022 Network Segmentation — applied to agent communication"
            -> identitySpoofing, communicationPoisoning

        # workflowLogging
            user info: "에이전트 워크플로우 상세 로깅 및 모니터링"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0020 Adversarial Detection, M0021 Audit Logging"
            -> obfuscateActionTrail, manipulateChatHistory
    }

    // Reasoning module for chain-of-thought and planning
    // OWASP Agentic T4, KC2
    asset ReasoningModule extends AIComponent {

        | connect
            user info: "추론 모듈에 대한 접근"
            developer info: "Access to the reasoning/planning component of the agent"
            -> manipulateReasoning, cascadingHallucination

        | manipulateReasoning
            user info: "추론 체인 조작으로 잘못된 결론 도달 유도 (OWASP Agentic T4, ATLAS AML.T0080)"
            developer info: "Adversary injects false premises to corrupt chain-of-thought reasoning"
            -> cascadingHallucination

        | cascadingHallucination
            user info: "추론 오류가 연쇄적으로 전파되는 할루시네이션 연쇄 (OWASP LLM09)"
            developer info: "One hallucination in reasoning chain triggers cascading false conclusions"

        | delayedInstruction
            user info: "추론 단계에서 지연 실행될 명령 삽입 (ATLAS AML.T0080.002)"
            developer info: "Instructions planted in reasoning context activate on future reasoning steps"

        # reasoningGuardrails
            user info: "추론 단계 검증 및 일관성 확인"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0004, M0008 — validate intermediate reasoning steps"
            -> manipulateReasoning, cascadingHallucination, delayedInstruction
    }

    // Memory module for agent persistent and working memory
    // OWASP Agentic KC4.1–KC4.6, T5–T7
    asset MemoryModule extends AIComponent {

        | access
            user info: "메모리 모듈 접근 (단기/장기/외부 메모리)"
            developer info: "Access to agent memory storage (in-context, episodic, semantic, external)"
            -> poisonMemory, exfiltrateMemory

        | poisonMemory
            user info: "에이전트 메모리 오염으로 지속적 행동 조작 (OWASP Agentic T5, ATLAS AML.T0080.001)"
            developer info: "Malicious content injected into agent memory persists across sessions"
            -> poisonThread, cascadePoisoning

        | poisonThread
            user info: "대화 스레드 오염으로 지속적 컨텍스트 조작 (OWASP Agentic T6)"
            developer info: "Thread-level memory poisoning affects all future interactions in that thread"
            -> cascadePoisoning

        | cascadePoisoning
            user info: "메모리 오염이 다른 에이전트나 세션으로 전파 (OWASP Agentic T7)"
            developer info: "Poisoned memory propagates to other agents or sessions sharing memory"

        | tamperEvidenceInMemory
            user info: "메모리 내 증거 삭제 또는 변조 (ATLAS AML.T0054.003)"
            developer info: "Adversary modifies memory contents to remove traces of malicious activity"

        | exfiltrateMemory
            user info: "에이전트 메모리 내 민감 정보 유출 (OWASP LLM02, OWASP Agentic T5)"
            developer info: "Sensitive data stored in agent memory (credentials, PII, secrets) exfiltrated"

        # memoryHardening
            user info: "메모리 무결성 보호 (체크섬, 버전 관리)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0007, M0014 — integrity checks on stored memory"
            -> poisonMemory, poisonThread, tamperEvidenceInMemory

        # memoryAccessControl
            user info: "메모리 접근 제어 및 격리 (세션/사용자 격리)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0005, M0022 — strict access control and memory isolation"
            -> access, exfiltrateMemory, cascadePoisoning
    }

    // Tool integration framework for external tool/API calls
    // OWASP Agentic KC3, T10–T12, OWASP LLM06
    asset ToolIntegrationFramework extends AIComponent {

        | connect
            user info: "도구 통합 프레임워크에 대한 접근"
            developer info: "Access to the tool invocation layer of the agent"
            -> unauthorizedToolInvocation, toolMisuse

        | unauthorizedToolInvocation
            user info: "권한 없는 도구 호출 (OWASP LLM06, OWASP Agentic T10)"
            developer info: "Agent invokes tools beyond its authorized scope without proper validation"
            -> dataExfiltration, dataDestruction, privilegeEscalation

        | toolMisuse
            user info: "도구를 의도하지 않은 방식으로 악용 (OWASP Agentic T11)"
            developer info: "Legitimate tools used in unintended ways to achieve malicious goals"
            -> dataExfiltration, unexpectedCodeExecution

        | dataExfiltration
            user info: "도구를 통한 데이터 유출 (ATLAS AML.T0025)"
            developer info: "Sensitive data exfiltrated via authorized external tool calls"

        | dataDestruction
            user info: "도구를 통한 데이터 삭제 또는 파괴 (ATLAS AML.T0101)"
            developer info: "Attacker uses AI agent tools to delete critical data or systems"

        | privilegeEscalation
            user info: "도구 호출을 통한 권한 상승 (OWASP Agentic T12, ATLAS AML.T0068)"
            developer info: "Leveraging tool permissions to escalate privileges beyond intended scope"
            -> credentialHarvesting

        | credentialHarvesting
            user info: "도구 실행 과정에서 자격증명 수집 (ATLAS AML.T0025.001)"
            developer info: "Credentials or API keys harvested during tool execution"

        | toolDataPoisoning
            user info: "도구 입력/출력 데이터 오염 (ATLAS AML.T0048)"
            developer info: "Data passed to/from tools manipulated to corrupt agent decision-making"

        | unexpectedCodeExecution
            user info: "도구 체인을 통한 예기치 않은 코드 실행 (ATLAS AML.T0099)"
            developer info: "Unintended code execution triggered through chained tool calls"

        # toolPermissions
            user info: "도구 호출 권한 최소화 (최소권한 원칙)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0018, M0022 — minimal permission set for each tool"
            -> unauthorizedToolInvocation, privilegeEscalation

        # restrictUntrustedDataToolInvocation
            user info: "신뢰할 수 없는 데이터 소스의 도구 호출 제한"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0004, M0005 — restrict tool calls triggered by untrusted input"
            -> toolMisuse, toolDataPoisoning, unexpectedCodeExecution

        # toolIOValidation
            user info: "도구 입력/출력 유효성 검증"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0015, M0017 — validate all tool inputs and outputs"
            -> toolDataPoisoning, unexpectedCodeExecution, dataExfiltration

        # humanApproval
            user info: "고위험 도구 호출에 대한 인간 승인 절차 (OWASP Agentic, Human-in-the-loop)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0018 User Training — require human approval for high-risk operations"
            -> dataDestruction, privilegeEscalation, unauthorizedToolInvocation
    }

    // External tools and services invoked by agents
    // OWASP Agentic KC3, ATLAS AML.T0099
    asset ExternalTool {

        | connect
            user info: "외부 도구/서비스에 대한 접근"
            developer info: "Network/API access to external tools (web search, code execution, APIs)"
            -> execute, commandExecution

        | execute
            user info: "외부 도구 실행"
            developer info: "Execution of external tool (file system, shell, web API, etc.)"
            -> commandExecution, dataLeak

        | commandExecution
            user info: "외부 도구를 통한 시스템 명령 실행 (ATLAS AML.T0099)"
            developer info: "OS commands executed via external tool invocation"
            -> codeInjection, reverseShell, escalatePrivilege

        | codeInjection
            user info: "코드 인젝션을 통한 임의 코드 실행 (ATLAS AML.T0099.001)"
            developer info: "Injected code executes in the context of the external tool"
            -> escapeToHost

        | reverseShell
            user info: "역방향 쉘 연결 생성 (ATLAS AML.T0099.002)"
            developer info: "Reverse shell established from tool execution environment to attacker"
            -> escapeToHost

        | escalatePrivilege
            user info: "도구 실행 환경에서의 권한 상승"
            developer info: "Local privilege escalation within tool execution environment"
            -> escapeToHost

        | escapeToHost
            user info: "샌드박스/컨테이너 탈출 (ATLAS AML.T0099.003)"
            developer info: "Escape from sandboxed tool execution environment to host system"

        | dataLeak
            user info: "외부 도구를 통한 데이터 유출"
            developer info: "Data exfiltrated through external tool's I/O channels"

        | publishPoisonedTool
            user info: "악성 코드가 포함된 도구를 공개 저장소에 배포 (OWASP LLM03)"
            developer info: "Compromised tool published to package registry for supply chain attack"

        # privilegedPermissions
            user info: "외부 도구 실행 권한 최소화"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0022 Network Segmentation, M0005 Control Access"
            -> commandExecution, escalatePrivilege, escapeToHost

        # toolSandboxing
            user info: "외부 도구 샌드박스 격리 실행"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0022 Network Segmentation — containerized/sandboxed execution"
            -> codeInjection, reverseShell, escapeToHost

        # restrictLibraryLoading
            user info: "외부 도구에서의 라이브러리 로딩 제한 (ATLAS M0010)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0010 Restrict Library Loading"
            -> codeInjection, publishPoisonedTool
    }

    // Agent configuration including credentials, tool definitions, prompts
    // OWASP Agentic KC5, T13–T15, OWASP LLM07
    asset AgentConfiguration {

        | access
            user info: "에이전트 설정 파일 또는 환경 접근"
            developer info: "Access to agent configuration (env files, config YAML, system prompt files)"
            -> extractCredentials, discoverConfiguration

        | extractCredentials
            user info: "설정에서 API 키, 비밀번호 등 자격증명 추출 (OWASP LLM07, ATLAS AML.T0025)"
            developer info: "Hardcoded or embedded credentials extracted from configuration"

        | discoverConfiguration
            user info: "에이전트 설정 내용 탐색 (OWASP Agentic T13)"
            developer info: "Reconnaissance of agent configuration to understand capabilities and constraints"
            -> discoverEmbeddedKnowledge, discoverToolDefinitions, discoverActivationTriggers

        | discoverEmbeddedKnowledge
            user info: "설정에 포함된 도메인 지식, 비즈니스 로직 탐색"
            developer info: "Extraction of embedded knowledge base, rules, or domain expertise"

        | discoverToolDefinitions
            user info: "에이전트 도구 목록 및 권한 탐색 (OWASP Agentic T14)"
            developer info: "Discovery of available tools and their parameter schemas for targeted exploitation"

        | discoverActivationTriggers
            user info: "특수 동작을 유발하는 트리거 탐색 (OWASP Agentic T15)"
            developer info: "Attacker probes for hidden activation triggers or special command keywords"

        | modifyConfiguration
            user info: "에이전트 설정 변조로 동작 조작"
            developer info: "Unauthorized modification of agent configuration parameters"
            -> accessUnsecuredCredentials

        | accessUnsecuredCredentials
            user info: "보안 처리 없이 저장된 자격증명 접근 (ATLAS AML.T0025.001)"
            developer info: "Plaintext credentials in config files accessed without encryption"

        # singleUserPermissions
            user info: "에이전트 설정 접근을 단일 서비스 계정으로 제한"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0005 Control Access to ML Models"
            -> access, modifyConfiguration, accessUnsecuredCredentials

        # encryptConfiguration
            user info: "설정 파일 암호화 및 비밀 관리 서비스 활용 (ATLAS M0019)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0019 Encrypt Sensitive Information — use secrets manager"
            -> extractCredentials, accessUnsecuredCredentials
    }
}

// ============================================================
// CATEGORY: RAGComponents
// Retrieval-Augmented Generation pipeline assets
// ============================================================

category RAGComponents {

    // RAG pipeline coordinating retrieval and augmented generation
    // OWASP LLM08, ATLAS AML.T0070, AML.T0071
    asset RAGPipeline extends AIComponent {

        | connect
            user info: "RAG 파이프라인에 대한 초기 접근"
            developer info: "Access to the RAG pipeline (document ingestion or retrieval endpoints)"
            -> poisonRetrieval, gatherIndexedTargets

        | poisonRetrieval
            user info: "검색 파이프라인 오염으로 악성 컨텍스트 주입 (ATLAS AML.T0070)"
            developer info: "Attacker poisons retrieval results to inject malicious context into LLM"
            -> craftRetrievalContent

        | gatherIndexedTargets
            user info: "인덱싱된 문서 목록 탐색 (ATLAS AML.T0007.001)"
            developer info: "Reconnaissance to identify what documents are indexed in vector store"
            -> craftRetrievalContent

        | craftRetrievalContent
            user info: "검색 결과를 조작하기 위한 콘텐츠 제작 (ATLAS AML.T0071)"
            developer info: "Carefully crafted content designed to be retrieved and manipulate LLM"
            -> harvestCredentials

        | harvestCredentials
            user info: "RAG 파이프라인을 통한 자격증명 수집 (ATLAS AML.T0025)"
            developer info: "Sensitive credentials retrieved and leaked through RAG context"

        # documentValidation
            user info: "문서 수집 전 유효성 검증 (형식, 스키마, 콘텐츠 필터링)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0015 Adversarial Input Detection — validate ingested documents"
            -> poisonRetrieval, craftRetrievalContent

        # documentProvenance
            user info: "문서 출처 추적 및 신뢰도 검증"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0013 Code Signing — provenance tracking for ingested documents"
            -> poisonRetrieval, harvestCredentials
    }

    // Vector database storing embeddings for retrieval
    // OWASP LLM08, ATLAS AML.T0070, AML.T0071
    asset VectorDatabase extends AIComponent {

        | access
            user info: "벡터 데이터베이스에 대한 접근"
            developer info: "Direct database access to vector store"
            -> injectFalseEntry, ragPoisoning, dataLeakage

        | injectFalseEntry
            user info: "가짜 벡터 엔트리 삽입으로 검색 결과 조작 (ATLAS AML.T0071)"
            developer info: "False entries injected into vector DB surface during retrieval to poison LLM"
            -> ragPoisoning

        | ragPoisoning
            user info: "RAG 인덱스 전체 오염 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0070, OWASP LLM08)"
            developer info: "Systematic poisoning of vector DB to corrupt all RAG-augmented responses"

        | dataLeakage
            user info: "벡터 DB에서 민감 정보 유출 (OWASP LLM02, LLM08)"
            developer info: "Sensitive data stored as embeddings extracted or inferred"

        | crossContextLeakage
            user info: "다른 사용자/세션의 컨텍스트 데이터 접근 (OWASP LLM08)"
            developer info: "Cross-tenant data leakage through shared vector space"

        | embeddingInversion
            user info: "저장된 임베딩에서 원본 텍스트 역추론 (OWASP LLM08, ATLAS AML.T0024)"
            developer info: "Inversion attack on stored embeddings to recover original document contents"

        # vectorDBAccessControl
            user info: "벡터 DB 접근 제어 (테넌트 격리, 인증)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0005, M0022 — per-tenant isolation and strict access control"
            -> access, crossContextLeakage, dataLeakage

        # vectorEncryption
            user info: "벡터 데이터 암호화 (저장 중 및 전송 중)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0019 Encrypt Sensitive Information"
            -> dataLeakage, embeddingInversion

        # inputSanitization
            user info: "벡터 DB 입력 데이터 정제 및 검증"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0015, M0007 — sanitize all data before vectorization and storage"
            -> injectFalseEntry, ragPoisoning
    }
}

// ============================================================
// CATEGORY: Infrastructure
// Infrastructure-level AI system assets
// ============================================================

category Infrastructure {

    // API endpoint exposing AI model capabilities
    // OWASP LLM10, ATLAS AML.T0040, AML.T0029
    asset APIEndpoint extends AIComponent {

        | connect
            user info: "AI API 엔드포인트에 대한 초기 접근"
            developer info: "Initial access to public or internal AI API endpoint"
            -> modelInferenceAccess, costHarvesting, denialOfService

        | modelInferenceAccess
            user info: "모델 추론 API 무단 접근 (ATLAS AML.T0040)"
            developer info: "Unauthorized access to model inference endpoint"
            -> promptInfiltration, spamChaff

        | costHarvesting
            user info: "API 호출 비용 과다 발생 (OWASP LLM10)"
            developer info: "Attacker generates excessive API calls to cause financial damage to operator"

        | denialOfService
            user info: "API 서비스 거부 공격 (OWASP LLM10, ATLAS AML.T0029)"
            developer info: "Flood of requests overwhelms API causing service unavailability"

        | spamChaff
            user info: "의미없는 대량 쿼리로 실제 공격 은폐 (ATLAS AML.T0040.001)"
            developer info: "Spam queries used to hide real attack queries in API logs"

        | promptInfiltration
            user info: "API를 통한 프롬프트 인젝션 공격 전달"
            developer info: "Adversarial prompts delivered via API to manipulate backend LLM"

        | apiAbuse
            user info: "API 악용 (권한 초과 접근, 정책 위반)"
            developer info: "API used in ways that violate terms of service or exceed authorization"

        # queryRateLimiting
            user info: "API 요청 속도 및 횟수 제한 (ATLAS M0004)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0004 Restrict Number of ML Model Queries"
            -> costHarvesting, denialOfService, spamChaff

        # apiAccessControl
            user info: "API 키 관리, 인증, 인가 제어"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0005 Control Access to ML Models, M0018 User Training"
            -> connect, modelInferenceAccess, apiAbuse
    }

    // AI software supply chain (models, datasets, libraries, containers)
    // OWASP LLM03, ATLAS AML.T0019
    asset AISupplyChain {

        | access
            user info: "AI 공급망 컴포넌트에 대한 접근"
            developer info: "Access to supply chain components (package repos, model hubs, data sources)"
            -> compromiseSoftware, compromiseModel, compromiseData

        | compromiseSoftware
            user info: "AI 프레임워크 또는 라이브러리 오염 (OWASP LLM03, ATLAS AML.T0010)"
            developer info: "Malicious code injected into AI framework or dependency library"
            -> maliciousPackage

        | compromiseModel
            user info: "사전학습 모델 또는 파인튜닝 모델 오염 (OWASP LLM03, ATLAS AML.T0019)"
            developer info: "Backdoored or poisoned model distributed through model supply chain"

        | compromiseData
            user info: "학습/평가 데이터셋 오염 (ATLAS AML.T0019.000)"
            developer info: "Poisoned datasets distributed through data supply chain"

        | compromiseContainer
            user info: "AI 서비스 컨테이너 이미지 오염 (ATLAS AML.T0010.001)"
            developer info: "Malicious code embedded in Docker/OCI container images for AI services"

        | maliciousPackage
            user info: "악성 패키지 공개 저장소 배포 (ATLAS AML.T0019.002, OWASP LLM03)"
            developer info: "Typosquatting or dependency confusion attack via malicious package"

        # aiBOM
            user info: "AI 소프트웨어 자재 명세서 (AI-BOM) 관리 (OWASP LLM03)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0013, M0016 — maintain complete inventory of AI dependencies"
            -> compromiseSoftware, maliciousPackage

        # supplyChainVerification
            user info: "공급망 컴포넌트 무결성 검증 (ATLAS M0014)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0014 Verify ML Artifacts — hash verification, provenance checks"
            -> compromiseModel, compromiseData, compromiseContainer

        # vulnerabilityScanning
            user info: "AI 공급망 취약점 스캔 (ATLAS M0016)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0016 Vulnerability Scanning"
            -> compromiseSoftware, maliciousPackage

        # supplyChainCodeSigning
            user info: "공급망 코드 서명 검증 (ATLAS M0013)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0013 Code Signing for all supply chain artifacts"
            -> maliciousPackage, compromiseSoftware, compromiseContainer
    }

    // User-facing interface (chat UI, voice, API client)
    // OWASP LLM01, ATLAS AML.T0047
    asset UserInterface {

        | access
            user info: "사용자 인터페이스에 대한 접근"
            developer info: "Access to the user-facing interface of the AI system"
            -> injectMaliciousInput, phishing

        | injectMaliciousInput
            user info: "사용자 인터페이스를 통한 악성 입력 삽입 (OWASP LLM01)"
            developer info: "Adversarial input submitted through chat UI or API client"

        | phishing
            user info: "AI를 활용한 피싱 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0047)"
            developer info: "Phishing attacks enhanced by AI-generated content"
            -> llmAssistedPhishing, socialEngineering

        | llmAssistedPhishing
            user info: "LLM을 활용한 고도화된 피싱 메시지 생성 (ATLAS AML.T0047.000)"
            developer info: "LLM used to generate convincing personalized phishing content"

        | deepfakeAttack
            user info: "딥페이크 오디오/비디오를 이용한 사회공학 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0047.001)"
            developer info: "Synthetic media used to impersonate trusted individuals"
            -> socialEngineering

        | socialEngineering
            user info: "AI 지원 사회공학 공격 (ATLAS AML.T0047)"
            developer info: "AI-assisted social engineering to manipulate users"

        | clickbait
            user info: "AI 생성 클릭베이트를 통한 악성 링크 유도"
            developer info: "AI-generated engaging content tricks users into clicking malicious links"

        # userSecurityTraining
            user info: "사용자 보안 인식 교육 (ATLAS M0018)"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0018 User Training — educate users about AI-specific threats"
            -> phishing, llmAssistedPhishing, socialEngineering, clickbait

        # deepfakeDetection
            user info: "딥페이크 탐지 기술 적용"
            developer info: "ATLAS M0020 Adversarial Detection — apply deepfake detection"
            -> deepfakeAttack
    }
}

// ============================================================
// ASSOCIATIONS
// Relationships between AI system assets
// ============================================================

associations {

    // LLM ↔ Memory: LLM uses memory modules for context persistence
    GenerativeLanguageModel [generativeLanguageModels] * <-- UsesMemory --> * [memoryModules] MemoryModule

    // LLM ↔ Orchestration: LLM is controlled by orchestration engine
    GenerativeLanguageModel [generativeLanguageModels] * <-- OrchestratedBy --> * [orchestrationEngines] OrchestrationEngine

    // LLM ↔ Reasoning: LLM delegates to reasoning module for CoT
    GenerativeLanguageModel [generativeLanguageModels] * <-- Reasons --> * [reasoningModules] ReasoningModule

    // LLM ↔ Tool Framework: LLM calls external tools through framework
    GenerativeLanguageModel [generativeLanguageModels] * <-- CallsTools --> * [toolIntegrationFrameworks] ToolIntegrationFramework

    // LLM ↔ RAG Pipeline: LLM augmented by retrieved context
    GenerativeLanguageModel [generativeLanguageModels] * <-- AugmentedBy --> * [ragPipelines] RAGPipeline

    // LLM ↔ Training Data: LLM trained on datasets
    GenerativeLanguageModel [generativeLanguageModels] * <-- TrainedOn --> * [trainingData] TrainingData

    // LLM ↔ Model Artifact: LLM implemented as model weights/artifact
    GenerativeLanguageModel [generativeLanguageModels] 1 <-- ImplementedAs --> 1 [modelArtifacts] ModelArtifact

    // LLM ↔ API Endpoint: LLM exposed through API endpoints
    GenerativeLanguageModel [generativeLanguageModels] * <-- ExposedThrough --> * [apiEndpoints] APIEndpoint

    // Embedding ↔ RAG: Embedding model serves the RAG pipeline
    EmbeddingModel [embeddingModels] * <-- EmbeddedBy --> * [ragPipelines] RAGPipeline

    // Embedding ↔ VectorDB: Embeddings stored in vector database
    EmbeddingModel [embeddingModels] * <-- StoresIn --> * [vectorDatabases] VectorDatabase

    // RAG ↔ VectorDB: RAG pipeline queries vector database
    RAGPipeline [ragPipelines] * <-- QueriesFrom --> * [vectorDatabases] VectorDatabase

    // Tool Framework ↔ External Tools: Framework invokes external tools
    ToolIntegrationFramework [toolIntegrationFrameworks] * <-- Invokes --> * [externalTools] ExternalTool

    // Tool Framework ↔ Configuration: Tool framework configured by agent config
    ToolIntegrationFramework [toolIntegrationFrameworks] * <-- ConfiguredBy --> * [agentConfigurations] AgentConfiguration

    // Orchestration ↔ Memory: Orchestration engine manages memory
    OrchestrationEngine [orchestrationEngines] * <-- AccessesMemory --> * [memoryModules] MemoryModule

    // Orchestration ↔ Configuration: Orchestration uses agent configuration
    OrchestrationEngine [orchestrationEngines] * <-- Uses --> * [agentConfigurations] AgentConfiguration

    // Orchestration ↔ Tool Framework: Orchestration controls tool execution
    OrchestrationEngine [orchestrationEngines] * <-- Controls --> * [toolIntegrationFrameworks] ToolIntegrationFrameworks ToolIntegrationFramework

    // Reasoning ↔ Memory: Reasoning module reads from memory
    ReasoningModule [reasoningModules] * <-- ReadsFrom --> * [memoryModules] MemoryModule

    // Supply Chain ↔ Model Artifact: Supply chain provides model artifacts
    AISupplyChain [aiSupplyChains] * <-- Provides --> * [modelArtifacts] ModelArtifact

    // Supply Chain ↔ Training Data: Supply chain provides training datasets
    AISupplyChain [aiSupplyChains] * <-- ProvidesData --> * [trainingData] TrainingData

    // Supply Chain ↔ External Tools: Supply chain provides tool libraries
    AISupplyChain [aiSupplyChains] * <-- ProvidesTools --> * [externalTools] ExternalTool

    // User Interface ↔ API Endpoint: UI communicates through API
    UserInterface [userInterfaces] * <-- AccessesThrough --> * [apiEndpoints] APIEndpoint

    // User Interface ↔ LLM: User directly interacts with LLM
    UserInterface [userInterfaces] * <-- InteractsWith --> * [generativeLanguageModels] GenerativeLanguageModel
}
